I’ll call it series in blue, Vol. 2.

Enjoy.

summary: When did u know Chris was the one.
question: When did u know Chris was the one.
answer: It all started a few years ago when I was staying the night at my best friends house. She was already on thin ice since her family didn’t own any wash cloths but she said she’ll make it up to me by putting on a movie called The Perfect Score, because I am a whore for movies, and as soon as she put it in, I went straight too my phone. It wasn’t until I glanced up and saw him. Now, my first reaction was utter confusion. I wasn’t interested in boys or girls at the time because #skhoolizlyfe but why did my heart skip a beat? Why was I suddenly so invested in this movie when I knew it was ass? I had to get down to the bottom of this! So, the next day I came home and thanked the heavens that it was just me and I made a beeline to my room, went to my desktop and did my research. This was all out of curiosity right? I wasn’t into anyone at the time remember? But every time he spoke in an interview, I got a little hot under the collar and the deeper I explored, the deeper my curiosity got until I finally came to turns that I, in fact, had a crush on a white man. I accepted that fact about myself that same night, especially after finding photo shoots of him shirtless(y’all know which one I’m talking about) After that, I spent the remainder of the night watching YouTube videos and [REDACTED] my pillow to the thought of him- *call dropped*
